fields.title: Spacious family cottage 45 mins from GTA!
fields.content: A rustic family lake house with modern touches. Comfortable beds, games, hot tub, ice fishing, boating and more. The perfect family getaway. Large enough to comfortably accommodate 2 families.

fields.title: $0 Cleaning Fee - 10 Min walk to Stampede!
fields.content: Our home is a 10-15 min walk from the Stampede Grounds and is located in the prime Ramsay/Inglewood neighbourhood. Situated on a quiet street three blocks south of 9th avenue where all the best local bars, restaurants and nightlife. The home features a private entrance, 3 queen bedrooms, 1 King Bed Loft, 1 queen pullout couch, 4 full bathrooms, 2 full kitchens, 2 living rooms, dinning room, and 2 in-suite laundry sets. You will also have access to a private backyard with a BBQ and patio set.

fields.title: ADIRONDACK LUXURY VILLA WITH HOTUB (NEW BUILD)
fields.content:
This brand-new luxurious property features floor to ceiling Marvin windows with with built-in hot tub and outdoor propane fireplace overlooking the glorious lake and mountain scenery!

The all-white modern interior boasts high-end appliances and fixtures making your stay a true luxury escape. High end ‘TheCompanyStore’ bedding! Gourmet kitchen with 6 burner Zline gas stove, convection oven, built in fridge/freezer drawers and an Insta Hot water faucet for tea lovers. Smart auto flush toilet!

fields.title: Timber Haven
fields.content: Reconnect with nature at this unforgettable timber frame tiny home. Nestled along the edge of the forest, overlooking a pond, this newly constructed home features a full kitchen, bathroom, private deck, hot tub, and stone patio with fire pit.  Sleeping loft accessible by ladder comfortably sleeps four with expansive views of nature.

fields.title: Escape North to Muskoka A-Frame | 4-Season Chalet
fields.content: Welcome to Muskoka A-frame, the perfect couple’s getaway or solo retreat, nestled in beautiful Hidden Valley. This classic 70’s A-frame has been re-imagined for the modern world. Wake up to swaying treetops, make gourmet meals & relax by the fire, with 2-story forest views.

fields.title: Full Service Villa / ATELIER ArtVillas Costa Rica
fields.content: All accommodation BREAKFAST INCLUDED Transcend the boundaries between inside and outside. Slide open the walls, slip through, and behold the striking expanse of the outside world. Just above beautiful beach with ocean view and jungle setting. Just published in Wall Paper, Dezeen etc etc.  We are only 1km from the main road and beach on a steep unpaved road hill, giving you superb ocean view but you need 4x4 car for access. All rooms are A/C

fields.title: Architectural Masterpiece | Best View in Telluride
fields.content: Prepare to be blown away by the exquisite architecture and views that just don't stop.  WE GUARANTEE THIS WILL BE THE MOST AMAZING AIRBNB EVER!  This modern mountain home was just remodeled and sits on over 2 acres. It is nestled in an aspen forest making it the perfect place to get away from it all, yet it is less than 5 miles from the heart of Telluride and only 3 miles to the free Mountain Village parking garage with ski-in/ski-out access and a free gondola that drops you right into Telluride
